I use many of these mods, and it looks like USI (USITools, AT_Utils and Firespitter) all cause the game to crash when loading. Removing all three allowed the game to load and play without issue
Thanks vedrit!! that was it. I removed Firespitter and now it works. Thanks a lot!!

I use AT_Utils1.4.4 and USITools 10.1.0  for ksp1.3.1 and firespitter 7.6

with no crashing FYI

and yes this is a Mod Conflict and as always check for the latest updates to fix. If the mod is not 1.3.1 updated then I tend not to use them
